#

Grilled Chicken with Steamed Broccoli

25 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

HealthyQuickGrilling

Description

Tender grilled chicken paired with vibrant steamed broccoli, perfect for a healthy, quick meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
